=Episode 13=

17
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,230
Be careful. Be careful.

18
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,350
Yuan?

19
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:47,710
Are you feeling better?

20
00:01:48,230 --> 00:01:50,120
Thanks to you, she kept throwing up.

21
00:01:50,510 --> 00:01:52,070
What do you mean thanks to me?

22
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:53,710
I didn’t know my pizza was spoiled.

23
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:55,070
Besides,

24
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,000
I suffered as much, all right?

25
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:59,590
Be careful next time.
Clean out your fridge

26
00:01:59,590 --> 00:02:01,230
and don’t eat expired food anymore.

27
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,000
Do you hear him, Bawan?

28
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,790
I’m telling you.

29
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:05,510
Ye Jingxi.

30
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,070
Yes?

31
00:02:07,430 --> 00:02:08,310
In fact,

32
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:11,910
Ms. Hua sent us.

33
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,590
Ye Jingxi.

34
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:17,630
Call me Bear.

35
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,520
Bear.

36
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:20,800
Mm.

37
00:02:21,710 --> 00:02:22,960
Perhaps,

38
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:25,280
we were thinking too simply,

39
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,590
without considering the consequence.

40
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,840
So,

41
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,910
you must listen to Ms. Hua.

42
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:29,800
Do whatever she asks you to,

43
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,280
and don’t try to resist. Got it?

44
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,150
I see.

45
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:36,120
You’re now working for my company, too?

46
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,870
What are you talking about?

47
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:39,590
We’re serious.

48
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:41,680
At first,

49
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,240
I thought

50
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,560
you loved to snub,

51
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,630
simply because you were a star.

52
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,870
But now,

53
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:48,870
I know life isn’t easy for you, either.

54
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:51,470
Work hard. I think highly of you.

55
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:53,750
Humph.

56
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:54,630
Humph?

57
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:55,520
What?

58
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,360
Bed No.1, time for injection.

59
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:58,960
Oh.

60
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:03,910
I’ll get the injection.

61
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,400
Injection? Oh, yes. I’ll leave.

62
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:19,710
Why don’t you leave?

63
00:03:19,710 --> 00:03:20,800
We’re all men. Why are you embarrassed?

64
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:27,560
We’re not your fans.
We won’t take photos of you.

65
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,800
Be quick. Take off your pants.

66
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:29,680
Turn around.

67
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,590
Nurse, give him the injection carefully.

68
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,030
Thank you.

69
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,310
He has fair skin.

70
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:45,590
Press it.

71
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:46,840
Thank you. Thank you.

72
00:03:47,590 --> 00:03:48,000
Well,

73
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,870
you have a good shape.

74
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,030
See? I trained him.

75
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:55,680
I don’t think he looks stronger than me.

76
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:56,800
What?

77
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,030
You’ve got a good shape, too?

78
00:03:58,430 --> 00:03:59,680
Why not take off your clothes
and compete with him?

79
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,430
How do you feel now?

80
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,400
Any better?

81
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,590
Though you two

82
00:04:11,150 --> 00:04:12,470
have seen

83
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:13,840
my hips,

84
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,630
it doesn’t mean

85
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:16,750
you can threaten me.

86
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,630
How do you know
we didn’t take photos of you?

87
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:20,480
How dare you!

88
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,160
Why don’t we dare?

89
00:04:25,310 --> 00:04:25,830
Be careful.

90
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,950
This time...

91
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:30,390
Mm?

92
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,800
I’m grateful to you.

93
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:33,510
But,

94
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:35,390
as for Yuan...

95
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:36,560
I know what you mean.

96
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:37,600
All right.

97
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,480
I’ll get to the point, then.

98
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,270
I know you always stop me

99
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:41,680
from staying with Yuan alone.

100
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:42,270
Yes.

101
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,310
I admit that.

102
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,000
You’re straightforward.

103
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,750
I also know that

104
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:50,240
you help me with study

105
00:04:50,950 --> 00:04:52,160
so that you can keep an eye on me.

106
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,830
Time’s limited. Get to the point.

107
00:04:53,830 --> 00:04:54,920
The point is

108
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,750
I like Yuan Caixi.

109
00:04:56,630 --> 00:04:57,680
So do I.

110
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,480
I’m sorry,

111
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:01,480
but I love her most.

112
00:05:02,950 --> 00:05:04,070
I grew up with her.

113
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:05,430
She and I have a lot in common.

114
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,800
No offense,

115
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:08,720
but I carried her on my back, hugged her,
and carried her on my shoulder.

116
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:12,480
What are you doing?

117
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:14,120
When I count from three to one,

118
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,420
-let go of me! Do you hear me?
-You’re not convinced?

119
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,750
Three, two, one.

120
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:18,430
It hurts! It hurts!

121
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:20,510
What? You get cocky, huh?

122
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:21,800
I’m a patient.

123
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,310
I’m still lying in bed.

124
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:24,920
You’re a patient, so what?

125
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,920
I just got an inspection. Let go of me.

126
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,430
You weak men,
what do you want to do?

127
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:29,720
Fight against me?

128
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,750
You know what?

129
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:32,750
Even if you fight me together,
you can’t hurt me.

130
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,920
If you’re not convinced, hold it in!

131
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,070
Li He,

132
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:38,270
you must understand.

133
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,920
Even you hugged her,
carried her on your back and shoulder,

134
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:42,070
that was because she was poisoned, hurt

135
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:43,240
and got stuck in fire.

136
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:43,830
Don’t take that seriously.

137
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:45,390
Even if you and she
have a lot in common,

138
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,240
she and I have common memories, too.

139
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,310
Get your hands off me!

140
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:51,390
You’re both unconvinced, right?

141
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,680
How can you two

142
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:54,600
make her feel safe?

143
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,190
Ah?

144
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,630
If you’re unconvinced,

145
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:58,120
compete with me like a man does.

146
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:58,630
Okay.

147
00:05:58,630 --> 00:05:59,120
Come on.

148
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,680
Come on. I must compete with you today.

149
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,430
Come on.

150
00:06:01,430 --> 00:06:02,600
Get off the bed.

151
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,160
Show me what you can do.

152
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,160
Childish boys.

153
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,240
Stand there.

154
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:05,830
What shall we compete?

155
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:06,480
Arm wrestling.

156
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:07,750
-Come on.
-Come on.

157
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:08,190
Wait.

158
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:08,870
Finished?

159
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:10,120
We’re worried about you.

160
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:12,160
Jingxi, have a good rest
and get well soon.

161
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:13,680
We can’t do without you.

162
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,270
Yes, yes.

163
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,660
It’s okay. It’s okay.

164
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:16,720
-Are you alright now?
-Yes.

165
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,310
Drink more hot water.

166
00:06:17,310 --> 00:06:18,750
Why is he standing already?

167
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:21,160
I’m going back tomorrow.

168
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:23,600
-So early? Don’t be in a hurry.
-Not early.

169
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,950
All right, you two.

170
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,600
Let him have some rest.

171
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,480
We should leave now.

172
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,390
-You’re right.
-Yes.

173
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:30,310
Be quick. Have some rest.

174
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:31,310
Lie down in bed.

175
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,040
Have some rest.

176
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,160
Be gentle. Be gentle.

177
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,240
Don’t catch a cold again.

178
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,750
-You finally get better.
-Tuck the quilt.

179
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:37,430
Remember to drink more hot water.

180
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,160
Get your face in, too.

181
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:40,480
-We’ll wait for you.
-Bye-bye.

182
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:42,510
-Have some good rest.
-He knows. Don’t worry.

183
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:44,000
I haven’t finished yet.

184
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:45,160
Bye-bye, Yuan.

185
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:56,120
Looks like Ms. Hua worries
for a right reason.

186
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,630
We should consider the consequence.

187
00:06:58,510 --> 00:06:59,240
Yeah.

188
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:00,920
Let’s get back home first.

189
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,310
Li He,

190
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,680
what’s bothering your little mind?

191
00:07:25,510 --> 00:07:26,430
I’m thinking that

192
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,510
Ms. Hua made a sense today.

193
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:30,870
Ye Jingxi is nearly of our age,

194
00:07:31,510 --> 00:07:32,750
but he has to bear so much.

195
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:34,720
Come on.

196
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,430
Whose little mind do you mean?

197
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,830
Ye Jingxi is nearly of our age,

198
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:42,160
but he’s decided his future long ago.

199
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,270
When he does what he wants,

200
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,430
he has to bear a lot.

201
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,480
You’re right.

202
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:48,950
What about you?

203
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:50,750
Do your parents know

204
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,160
you like programming?

205
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,600
Even if they do, they won’t support me.

206
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,000
What’re you going to do, then?

207
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,390
No idea.

208
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:02,270
If only I could do what I want

209
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,870
like you and Ye Jingxi do!

210
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:07,720
If someone were as smart as you,
he could do everything.

211
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,830
But I’m confused.

212
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:12,000
Why do your parents force you

213
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,360
to be a lawyer?

214
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,480
Thanks for the compliment, Li He.

215
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,240
My parents always want me

216
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:20,560
to live my life as they have planned.

217
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:22,040
No deviation is allowed.

218
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,950
Don’t bother about me.
Let’s talk about you.

219
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:27,680
Running is good.
What’s your plan for the future?

220
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,430
I made a deal

221
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,120
with Lin Chuan and other teammates that

222
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,440
we’ll keep running

223
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,630
in Haiwen Sport University.

224
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:35,360
Haiwen Sport University?

225
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:35,960
Yep.

226
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,870
You’re doing better in study now.

227
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,750
You can have better choices, can’t you?

228
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,440
I don’t care
which university I’ll study in

229
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:44,510
as long as I can keep running.

230
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,080
You should at least
have a plan for running.

231
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,550
Don’t you want to study
in a better university?

232
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:51,630
Come on.

233
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,120
Do all good students like you
talk like that?

234
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,550
Monitor said something similar.

235
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:58,910
Maybe she and I think alike.

236
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,240
No way.

237
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:02,270
She cares about me.
It’s none of your business.

238
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,870
Then you should think
more carefully about it.

239
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:06,440
Don’t let her down.

240
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,080
Don’t worry.
I’ll think carefully about it.

241
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:11,600
You’d better care more about yourself.

242
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:29,600
Why are you coming back so late?

243
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:31,600
Oh.

244
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,550
I’m back late for some reason.

245
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:35,720
Mom, what’re you doing in my room?

246
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,910
I’m folding your clothes.

247
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,240
Were you going through my stuff?

248
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,480
I wasn’t.

249
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,960
I had planned to clean your desk.

250
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,480
What are you talking about?

251
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:48,720
By the way,

252
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,320
today is Sunday.

253
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,030
Where have you been,

254
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:52,870
instead of studying at home?

255
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,000
I...

256
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:57,150
I was with friends.

257
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,790
Friends?

258
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,200
Why are you wasting your time with friends
at such a critical moment?

259
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:05,440
Are you getting close to Li He lately?

260
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,840
He’s a PE student.

261
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:09,600
It’s okay
if he doesn’t do well in study.

262
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,200
But you’re different.

263
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,600
It’s not true.

264
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,120
He’s studying very hard, too.

265
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:15,200
How dare you talk back!

266
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,390
This is a very critical moment for you.

267
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:19,030
You can’t even waste one single second.

268
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:20,840
But you keep playing around every day.

269
00:10:21,030 --> 00:10:22,240
Can you bear with the consequence?

270
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,200
I can.

271
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,630
I take responsibility for myself.

272
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:27,270
You!

273
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,600
How can you take responsibility?

274
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,200
How can you do that as a student?

275
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,720
Do you know what you’re talking about?

276
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,790
I do.

277
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:39,150
Zeyu, don’t always
get close to PE students

278
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:41,200
in case they mislead you.
Do you hear me?

279
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,600
What a boy!

280
