286
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:44,840
You’re looking at the notice
for parents’ meeting

287
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,440
and the application form.

288
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:48,550
Discuss with your families

289
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:50,720
about how to fill the form,

290
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,870
though it’s only for reference.

291
00:11:53,390 --> 00:11:55,120
You can take the chance

292
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,670
to talk with your parents

293
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,550
about your development
after graduation.

294
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,000
Class’s over.

295
00:12:02,260 --> 00:12:03,860
(Application Form for Universities)

296
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:05,270
Yuan,

297
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:06,720
how I envy you!

298
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:09,630
You’re good enough to be admitted
to Beikai University, right?

299
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:10,910
Don’t make fun of me.

300
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:12,240
What about you?
Which university do you want to go?

301
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:14,870
In fact,

302
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,910
I want to go to Zhongzhen.

303
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,630
Zhongzhen?

304
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:20,480
Zhongzhen University?

305
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:21,440
Yes.

306
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:24,360
Its Chinese Department is newly founded,

307
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:27,600
with new teachers
and teaching philosophies.

308
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,390
Mostly importantly,

309
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:31,120
it has the Creative Writing Course.

310
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:31,910
I really want to go.

311
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:32,630
It suits you.

312
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:35,080
You’re going to Zhongzhen?

313
00:12:36,510 --> 00:12:37,960
That’s too far.

314
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:43,150
I’m not even going to leave Haiwen.

315
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,080
Chief,

316
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:49,960
what about you?

317
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:51,750
We made a deal

318
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,200
to go to Haiwen Sport University, right?

319
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:55,600
I’ve filled my form.

320
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,030
Chief?

321
00:13:05,030 --> 00:13:05,630
Chief?

322
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:06,510
What?

323
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:09,910
Haiwen Sport University.

324
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,870
Oh, Haiwen Sport University.

325
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,390
Chief,

326
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,200
don’t tell me you changed your mind?

327
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,480
We made a deal three years ago.

328
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:24,000
We planned to go there
as early as we were in Grade 10.

329
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:26,320
You’ll be disloyal
if you change your mind now.

330
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,840
No. You’re thinking too much.

331
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:30,270
I was just lost in thought. Be seated.

332
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:32,910
I’ll fill the form.
Something’s just on my mind.

333
00:13:46,300 --> 00:13:49,740
(Application Form for Universities)

334
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:08,320
The air is so fresh.

335
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:10,840
What?

336
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:15,480
Want to be taken photos of
without makeup?

337
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,030
Get in the car, Jingxi.

338
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,030
Get in the car, Ms. Hua.

339
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,720
Surprise!

340
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:39,600
Isn’t it a surprise, super star?

341
00:14:39,790 --> 00:14:42,320
This isn’t a surprise, but a shock.

342
00:14:42,870 --> 00:14:44,240
We knew you left hospital today.

343
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,960
Then we asked Bawan for the key.

344
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:48,600
We came earlier
to prepare a surprise for you.

345
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:50,670
You haven’t seen us these days.

346
00:14:50,910 --> 00:14:52,200
We’ve been worrying about you.

347
00:14:52,390 --> 00:14:52,910
You have?

348
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:53,360
Yes.

349
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,030
You worried about me?

350
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:56,480
I... I certainly did.

351
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:57,910
How do you feel now? Any better?

352
00:14:57,910 --> 00:14:58,790
Are you alright now?

353
00:14:58,790 --> 00:14:59,550
-Li He.
-Don’t. Don’t.

354
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,440
I’m very well.

355
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:03,120
But you’ll hurt me again.

356
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:05,720
You were away lately.
In case you fall behind in study,

357
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:07,000
I’ve sorted out the papers,

358
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:10,080
homework and note for you.

359
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,360
Aren’t you moved?

360
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,270
I’m so moved.

361
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:16,360
It’s really my honor

362
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,840
to have good friends like you.

363
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,120
You’re welcome.

364
00:15:19,390 --> 00:15:20,320
And this.

365
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:22,120
Miss Luo asked me to bring this to you.

366
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:23,440
You must hand it in next week.

367
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,080
Application form?

368
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:26,550
Yep.

369
00:15:27,150 --> 00:15:27,600
Well,

370
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,960
you’ll go to Beijing Academy of Drama
or The Central Film Academy, right?

371
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:32,000
I want to study music, in fact.

372
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:33,670
Music?

373
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:34,750
Which university?

374
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:36,270
I haven’t decided yet.

375
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,240
Yuan, which university
do you want to go?

376
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,910
The Finance Department
of Beikai University.

377
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:42,390
There’ll be no problem.

378
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,630
You have such good marks.
You’ll easily be admitted.

379
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:47,120
There’s no problem
with Beikai University.

380
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:49,080
But it’ll be hard

381
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,270
if I want to go to Huatsing University
or Yanbei University.

382
00:15:50,270 --> 00:15:51,630
But Zeyu is different.

383
00:15:51,910 --> 00:15:54,030
Zeyu, which one do you want to go?

384
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:57,320
I haven’t decided yet.

385
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:59,000
But either will do.

386
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:01,030
It depends on my feeling.

387
00:16:01,550 --> 00:16:02,750
Your feeling?

388
00:16:03,030 --> 00:16:05,480
You think you can pick a university
like picking vegetables?

389
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:08,080
It’s not very different to me.

390
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,550
You know, I have quite high scores.

391
00:16:10,630 --> 00:16:11,120
All right.

392
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,960
Don’t bother about others.

393
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,200
You make people worry most.

394
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,120
Which university do you want to go?

395
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,480
Why do you worry about me?

396
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:20,550
I’m special in PE.

397
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:22,080
I’ve made stable progress in study.

398
00:16:22,390 --> 00:16:23,960
I can go to many universities.

399
00:16:24,270 --> 00:16:25,960
Which one do you like best?

400
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,670
I’ll think carefully about it.
Don’t worry, monitor.

401
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,270
It’s the afternoon.

402
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:02,120
The audition should have been finished.

403
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:05,160
Why hasn’t Ye Jingxi texted us yet?

404
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:11,750
Bear?

405
00:17:12,830 --> 00:17:13,680
How was the audition going?

406
00:17:14,110 --> 00:17:15,270
Smoothly.

407
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:17,350
The director said
I looked like a swimmer.

408
00:17:18,030 --> 00:17:20,070
Casting directors
were also satisfied with me.

409
00:17:20,510 --> 00:17:21,880
You mean you passed the audition?

410
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:25,440
No.

411
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,920
Don’t pull a long face.

412
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:34,270
That’s normal.

413
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:37,550
Many actors compete for one role.

414
00:17:39,030 --> 00:17:41,240
But we worked hard for a long time.

415
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:42,880
Others worked hard, too.

416
00:17:43,110 --> 00:17:44,000
Besides,

417
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:47,440
if I feel sad
every time I fail an audition,

418
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,640
how can I live my life?

419
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:51,270
It doesn’t matter.

420
00:17:51,270 --> 00:17:52,270
That’s fine.

421
00:17:52,270 --> 00:17:54,070
The final exam is coming.
Review your lessons carefully.

422
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:54,920
Yes.

423
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:55,960
I think so, too.

424
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:56,790
So,

425
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:58,310
Yuan.

426
00:17:58,310 --> 00:17:58,720
Mm?

427
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:00,030
Keep helping me with my study, okay?

428
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:01,000
Me?

429
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:01,480
Yes.

430
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:02,640
I’ll help you, too.

431
00:18:06,270 --> 00:18:07,070
So will I.

432
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:09,920
Yes.

433
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:11,400
We’ve made a deal.

434
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:13,510
Stand up. Let me talk to him.

435
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:16,680
We’ve set up a study group,

436
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:17,920
simply to study hard.

437
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:18,400
Mm.

438
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:20,880
Is that so?

439
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:22,790
-Yes.
-Yes.

440
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,000
Good.

441
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:27,310
Now you have a high awareness.

442
00:18:36,310 --> 00:18:38,270
Jingxi, Ms. Hua is coming.

443
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:39,640
She’s very angry, I think.

444
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:51,790
Ms. Hua, coming to visit me so late?

445
00:18:51,790 --> 00:18:53,240
I really appreciate that.

446
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:01,070
Ms. Hua,

447
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:02,550
shall I wait for you in the car?

448
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,400
Stay here.

449
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:04,920
You should also listen to

450
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:06,270
what I’m going to say.

451
00:19:18,830 --> 00:19:19,680
Artist

452
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,640
is an occupation.

453
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:25,400
There’re rules for every occupation.

454
00:19:28,070 --> 00:19:29,070
In the film audition,

455
00:19:29,510 --> 00:19:31,240
you deliberately behaved bad

456
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:33,350
so that you disappointed
the casting directors.

457
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:35,920
Have you thought of

458
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:37,400
what consequences

459
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:38,550
may be?

460
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,590
Don’t stare at him.

461
00:19:42,110 --> 00:19:43,720
You think I know no one

462
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:45,200
in the film company?

463
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:49,830
You don’t care if the audition video

464
00:19:49,830 --> 00:19:51,030
will be exposed

465
00:19:51,310 --> 00:19:53,480
or if your future will be influenced.

466
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:56,480
You neglected your duty

467
00:19:57,310 --> 00:19:58,350
as an artist.

468
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,680
Do you know how senior actors

469
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:03,790
became successful?

470
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:06,070
They’re devoted to work,

471
00:20:06,070 --> 00:20:07,640
and responsible.

472
00:20:08,310 --> 00:20:09,240
What about you?

473
00:20:09,790 --> 00:20:10,920
Ask yourself.

474
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:13,830
Have you fulfilled your duty?

475
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:17,070
I can’t fulfill that.

476
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,400
You always ask me to act in films.

477
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:22,110
I know you want to study
in a conservatory of music!

478
00:20:23,310 --> 00:20:24,640
But have you studied hard?

479
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:30,350
Do you think you’re different
from ordinary students,

480
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:32,510
you have privilege

481
00:20:32,510 --> 00:20:33,830
and you can pick any university,

482
00:20:34,030 --> 00:20:37,070
because you’re a little famous in China

483
00:20:37,790 --> 00:20:40,310
and everyone in the company
flatters you?

484
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,030
You’re young,

485
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:47,750
but impetuous!

486
00:20:48,310 --> 00:20:50,640
A little reputation makes you arrogant!

487
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,070
You want to study music?

488
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:02,480
Okay.

489
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:05,920
But you should study hard first

490
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:08,640
and pass the entrance examination
with your own strength.

491
00:21:09,350 --> 00:21:11,480
Now that you don’t want to be an actor,

492
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:14,510
you should make clear
what else you want to be

493
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:17,160
and how you can be it!

494
00:21:55,260 --> 00:22:00,100
(Minimum Score for all majors
of Haixing Conservatory of Music)

495
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:16,000
(Ms. Hua)
Ms. Hua,

496
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:18,160
I understand what you said.

497
00:22:19,550 --> 00:22:20,830
I was too childish.

498
00:22:22,510 --> 00:22:24,550
Please get me
a professional music teacher.

499
00:22:25,510 --> 00:22:27,030
I’ll study hard.

500
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:31,720
Monitor,

501
00:22:32,110 --> 00:22:34,310
collect the application forms
and send them to my office.

502
00:22:34,310 --> 00:22:35,880
-All right.
-Class’s over.

503
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:46,920
Yuan,

504
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:48,200
I have something to tell you.

505
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:49,000
What?

506
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:56,750
Let’s talk out of the classroom.

507
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:57,590
All right.

508
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:14,920
You two.

509
00:23:15,110 --> 00:23:17,160
Why do you always follow us around?

510
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:18,030
Don’t talk nonsense.

511
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:19,880
Why are you taking her out so seriously?

512
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:25,830
From tomorrow on,

513
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:27,960
I’ll ask for a two-week leave.

514
00:23:28,350 --> 00:23:29,240
Two weeks?

515
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,160
So long? What are you going to do?

516
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:31,830
Yeah.

517
00:23:33,240 --> 00:23:34,200
My company has arranged

518
00:23:34,590 --> 00:23:37,110
professional music training for me.

519
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:38,400
I must go.

520
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,880
What did I say?
You’re not talented in acting!

521
00:23:42,070 --> 00:23:43,830
You’d better work hard on music.

522
00:23:47,550 --> 00:23:48,640
Just... just kidding.

523
00:23:50,030 --> 00:23:52,070
Last night, Ms. Hua said a lot to me.

524
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:55,510
I have to admit that she’s right.

525
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:56,790
So,

526
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:58,350
I can no longer idle away my time.

527
00:23:59,240 --> 00:24:01,160
I must chase my music dream carefully.

528
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:05,790
What about school work?
Have you asked for a leave?

529
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:07,000
Yes.

530
00:24:07,590 --> 00:24:08,160
Go ahead.

531
00:24:08,270 --> 00:24:09,350
Don’t worry about school work.

532
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:10,830
We’ll leave notes to you.

533
00:24:13,750 --> 00:24:14,400
Thanks.

534
00:24:16,030 --> 00:24:16,590
All right.

535
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:18,070
That’s all?

536
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:19,790
Let’s go for lunch.

537
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,200
Come on.

538
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:22,880
Study hard.

539
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:30,200
Bai.

540
00:24:30,550 --> 00:24:31,160
What?

541
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,750
Come on.

542
00:24:36,160 --> 00:24:37,240
Let me show you a photo of a girl.

543
00:24:37,790 --> 00:24:38,550
What photo?

544
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:42,790
My family introduced her to me
last month.

545
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:43,750
Beautiful, isn’t she?

546
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:44,920
Looks good.

547
00:24:47,110 --> 00:24:48,350
She has fair skin,

548
00:24:48,350 --> 00:24:49,510
and big eyes.

549
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:50,790
And she’s tall.

550
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:53,240
She’s my cup of tea.

551
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,400
We make a perfect couple.

552
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:59,110
Shall I introduce you a girl, too?

553
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,590
-Me?
-Yes.

554
00:25:01,310 --> 00:25:02,550
Don’t bother. I’m doing alright.

555
00:25:03,270 --> 00:25:03,960
No.

556
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:06,200
You’re no longer young.
You need a girlfriend.

557
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:08,550
You should consider about that.

558
00:25:08,790 --> 00:25:10,310
No. No, I don’t.

559
00:25:11,270 --> 00:25:12,590
You know that.

560
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:14,960
It’s been long
since you last had a girlfriend.

561
00:25:15,350 --> 00:25:16,480
If I didn’t know you,

562
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:18,680
I would think
you have problems with love.

563
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:21,160
