567
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:27,720
Beautiful, isn’t she?

568
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:28,680
Looks good.

569
00:25:30,750 --> 00:25:31,750
How come?

570
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:33,350
Ridiculous!

571
00:25:35,570 --> 00:25:36,110
-Ridiculous?
-Oops.

572
00:25:36,110 --> 00:25:38,480
I said no, no, no!

573
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:39,680
Bai Fei!

574
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:43,590
Come over.

575
00:25:45,110 --> 00:25:46,550
I said no, didn’t I?

576
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,160
Ridiculous, isn’t he?

577
00:26:04,830 --> 00:26:05,590
What happened?

578
00:26:08,350 --> 00:26:08,920
Li He,

579
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:10,790
