580
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,830
I do. I’m not illiterate.

581
00:26:12,960 --> 00:26:14,480
Be serious. Don’t try to fool me.

582
00:26:16,310 --> 00:26:17,070
Ning Zeyu,

583
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:19,550
do you know how important
the application form is?

584
00:26:20,640 --> 00:26:21,240
I do.

585
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,070
It’s a starting point.

586
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:24,590
After filling it,

587
00:26:25,270 --> 00:26:26,830
we’ll work towards it

588
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,000
and study hard

589
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:28,880
so as to achieve our application.

590
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:29,720
All right.

591
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,440
Let me ask you again.

592
00:26:32,460 --> 00:26:33,540
(Information Engineering,
Tiangong University of Science and Technology)

593
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:34,920
You filled this form

594
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:36,030
by yourself?

595
00:26:40,030 --> 00:26:41,000
Yes.

596
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:43,790
I’m serious. I filled it carefully.

597
00:26:46,030 --> 00:26:47,790
-So, you really want to...
-So, you really want to...

598
00:26:47,790 --> 00:26:48,440
Tiangong.

599
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:49,030
Huatsing.

600
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:53,350
Zeyu,

601
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:56,020
I know

602
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:57,400
you’ve been an obedient boy.

603
00:26:58,720 --> 00:27:00,350
But you have a mind of your own.

604
00:27:03,070 --> 00:27:04,110
At your age,

605
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:07,000
you have the mind to rebel.
I can understand.

606
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:10,400
But you shouldn’t give vent on

607
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:12,350
by ruining your future.

608
00:27:13,200 --> 00:27:13,960
I don’t want to rebel.

609
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:15,880
I really want to go to Tiangong University
of Science and Technology.

610
00:27:20,590 --> 00:27:23,000
You chose that,
instead of Huatsing and Yanbei.

611
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,880
Do you families know?

612
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:29,110
Not yet.

613
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:31,030
But I will communicate with them.

614
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:35,070
-Zeyu.
-Miss Luo,

615
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:37,720
I really want to learn programming.

616
00:27:38,750 --> 00:27:39,670
Tiangong University is
China’s best university

617
00:27:39,670 --> 00:27:41,440
for programming.

618
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,030
In term of programming,

619
00:27:43,030 --> 00:27:44,720
I think it’s as good
as Huatsing and Yanbei.

620
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:47,480
I also don’t think
following my parents’ decision

621
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,350
can be the only right choice.

622
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:51,000
You also said,

623
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:54,310
do what you have to do,
till you can do what you want to do.

624
00:27:55,270 --> 00:27:56,440
This is my application form.

625
00:27:58,350 --> 00:27:59,790
I hope I can apply personally.

626
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:02,070
Huatsing!

627
00:28:02,350 --> 00:28:03,310
Huatsing!

628
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:04,440
Li He,

629
00:28:04,830 --> 00:28:06,750
I know you’re always confident
for no reason.

630
00:28:07,350 --> 00:28:09,070
There is a fine line

631
00:28:09,070 --> 00:28:10,350
between confidence
and excessive confidence.

632
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:12,000
Bai, that sounds absurd.

633
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:14,200
Others look down on me.
You also do?

634
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:16,790
I don’t mean that.

635
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:17,790
I...

636
00:28:19,310 --> 00:28:20,480
I just want to tell you that

637
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:22,510
it’s good to be ambitious.

638
00:28:22,510 --> 00:28:24,590
But there’s a gap
between ambition and reality.

639
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,480
There’s only one term

640
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,270
before the college entrance examination.

641
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:29,030
How can you be admitted to Huatsing
with existing scores?

642
00:28:29,350 --> 00:28:31,310
Why can’t I? I checked it.

643
00:28:31,480 --> 00:28:33,440
I can be a high-level athlete
for Huatsing.

644
00:28:33,750 --> 00:28:35,640
It’s hard to be admitted to Huatsing.

645
00:28:35,830 --> 00:28:37,480
But a high-level athlete
doesn’t need a score

646
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:39,350
as high as academic students.

647
00:28:39,480 --> 00:28:40,640
I can have a try.

648
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:43,030
It’s not that problem.

649
00:28:43,350 --> 00:28:43,790
Yes.

650
00:28:44,270 --> 00:28:46,790
Huatsing has preferential policies
for outstanding PE students.

651
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:48,830
But your score isn’t good enough.

652
00:28:49,590 --> 00:28:50,510
Do you know

653
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:52,510
if you fill the application improperly,

654
00:28:53,510 --> 00:28:55,590
you might be admitted to no university?

655
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:58,160
Bai,

656
00:28:58,480 --> 00:28:59,270
don’t worry.

657
00:28:59,830 --> 00:29:00,830
I’ll study hard

658
00:29:01,270 --> 00:29:02,030
and I will succeed.

659
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:05,070
Why do you think so?

660
00:29:11,030 --> 00:29:11,550
Monitor.

661
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:12,440
Enjoy the drumsticks.

662
00:29:13,310 --> 00:29:14,590
I won’t. They’re poisonous.

663
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:16,400
Why are they?

664
00:29:16,510 --> 00:29:17,590
I just bought them.

665
00:29:28,590 --> 00:29:29,200
Ah.

666
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:36,920
What trick are you trying to use?

667
00:29:38,510 --> 00:29:39,640
No trick.

668
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:41,680
Yuan,

669
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:43,400
could you be my private tutor again?

670
00:29:44,070 --> 00:29:44,750
For what subjects?

671
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:46,830
Chinese, Math, English,
Physics and Chemistry.

672
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:47,960
Help me with whatever
I don’t do well in.

673
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:49,720
Anytime and anywhere.

674
00:29:50,880 --> 00:29:52,030
Are you trying to make trouble again?

675
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:53,640
Listen. Let go of Mr. Ma.

676
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:54,550
It’s really hard for him.

677
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:55,830
I’m not trying to make trouble.

678
00:29:56,070 --> 00:29:57,110
I’m serious.

679
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,350
I want to study hard.

680
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:00,160
Study hard?

681
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:01,590
That’s what you said last time.

682
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:02,400
What?

683
00:30:12,790 --> 00:30:13,790
I want to go to Huatsing University.

684
00:30:18,160 --> 00:30:18,830
Li He,

685
00:30:18,830 --> 00:30:19,680
stop joking, all right?

686
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:21,000
It doesn’t sound funny at all.

687
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:22,550
I’m not joking.

688
00:30:23,590 --> 00:30:24,830
I want to be a high-level athlete

689
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:26,480
and go to Huatsing University.

690
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:29,350
High-level athlete?

691
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:30,400
What’s that?

692
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,480
A high-level athlete is the best

693
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:36,720
among PE students.

694
00:30:37,110 --> 00:30:38,480
He has to do well in sports,

695
00:30:38,830 --> 00:30:40,880
but his score
for the college entrance examination

696
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:43,920
must also be above 65%
of the second batch.

697
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:46,270
A high-level athlete can be admitted
to a comprehensive university,

698
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:48,350
more than a sport university.

699
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:49,440
So,

700
00:30:50,070 --> 00:30:51,160
to go to Huatsing University,

701
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:53,110
I must become a high-level athlete.

702
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:54,680
Do you understand?

703
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,750
Good, Li He.

704
00:30:57,350 --> 00:30:58,960
World champion.

705
00:30:59,590 --> 00:31:00,480
The future...

706
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:02,240
All right. The future world champion,

707
00:31:02,240 --> 00:31:03,920
I’m waiting to get your autograph.

708
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:05,400
No problem.

709
00:31:13,790 --> 00:31:14,310
How many seconds?

710
00:31:14,830 --> 00:31:15,960
Good job.

711
00:31:16,270 --> 00:31:17,640
You’ve made so much progress.

712
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:18,830
It’s no big deal.

713
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:19,550
Have some water.

714
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:22,110
Thank you, Chief.

715
00:31:22,110 --> 00:31:22,590
Yun Xiang.

716
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,350
Well done.

717
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:34,400
Oh, Lin Chuan,

718
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:37,510
I don’t think
I’ll go to Haiwen Sport University.

719
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:40,590
What?

720
00:31:44,590 --> 00:31:45,640
I want to apply for Huatsing University.

721
00:31:47,030 --> 00:31:47,830
Are you serious?

722
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:57,510
I didn’t care
which university I would go

723
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:00,200
as long as we could run together.

724
00:32:01,350 --> 00:32:02,070
But this time,

725
00:32:05,310 --> 00:32:06,790
I want to see how far I can go.

726
00:32:11,750 --> 00:32:12,270
All right.

727
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:15,030
It doesn’t matter.

728
00:32:15,310 --> 00:32:15,920
It’s your own decision, anyway.

729
00:32:17,510 --> 00:32:18,480
Don’t say that, Chuan.

730
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:20,750
I never forget what we promised.

731
00:32:22,070 --> 00:32:23,400
We can apply for it together.

732
00:32:23,750 --> 00:32:25,510
Let’s work hard
towards the biggest ambition.

733
00:32:25,510 --> 00:32:26,830
Stop explaining.

734
00:32:26,830 --> 00:32:27,920
If you can be admitted
to Huatsing University,

735
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,880
you’ll be the pride
of Sen Yong Sport Team.

736
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:31,880
I’ll be proud of you, too.

737
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:33,070
Chuan,

738
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:34,880
you can also apply for Huatsing.

739
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:37,200
You study the best

740
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,310
-among us four.
-I’m not going.

741
00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:39,510
Why don’t you go?

742
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:41,830
You also do the best in sports.

743
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:43,880
I think you know
why I must go to Haiwen Sport University.

744
00:32:52,030 --> 00:32:52,790
Wish you success!

745
00:33:15,790 --> 00:33:16,350
Chief,

746
00:33:16,720 --> 00:33:18,030
it’s a good thing
when you want to apply for Huatsing.

747
00:33:18,030 --> 00:33:18,960
We all support you.

748
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:20,200
But,

749
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:22,400
you know what we can do.

750
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:24,720
We may not even pass the sports exam,

751
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:26,070
not to mention
the college entrance examination.

752
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:30,590
Chief, we’re not going to the tutorial.

753
00:33:31,750 --> 00:33:34,480
See you at the training, Chief.

754
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:05,920
You’re back?

755
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:06,480
Mm.

756
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:09,000
I’ve got the material ready.

757
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:10,320
Mm.

758
00:34:12,550 --> 00:34:13,590
You come back alone?

759
00:34:14,030 --> 00:34:14,630
Yeah.

760
00:34:17,360 --> 00:34:19,000
It doesn’t matter, monitor.
Let’s get started.

761
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:23,030
Can I not do math problems today?

762
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:24,190
All right.

763
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:26,030
Let’s start from Chinese first.

764
00:35:05,420 --> 00:35:09,780
♪The distance between us
Changes all the time♪

765
00:35:10,940 --> 00:35:16,020
♪Just like the last dessert
Making me want more♪

766
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:21,180
♪I don’t dare to breathe anymore
In case you feel my heart♪

767
00:35:21,540 --> 00:35:26,100
♪Turn my back to you with courage♪

768
00:35:27,820 --> 00:35:30,300
♪The attraction of sight proves♪

769
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:32,590
Lin Chuan, shall we...

770
00:35:33,700 --> 00:35:37,980
♪The melody of the song
Fills our memories♪

771
00:35:39,260 --> 00:35:41,700
♪The note of the class
Is filled with secrets♪

772
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:43,800
Boys also bicker?

773
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:44,630
We’re not bickering.

774
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:45,510
No?

775
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:46,800
Then why are you here alone?

776
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:56,030
I thought PE students like you
are more open-minded.

777
00:35:56,150 --> 00:35:58,190
Turns out you’re not different from us.

778
00:36:12,980 --> 00:36:17,660
♪The problem between us
Can be solved by no formula♪

779
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:19,840
Why don’t you buy me dinner?

780
00:36:20,230 --> 00:36:21,550
After helping you for a long time,

781
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:23,190
I’m starving.

782
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:29,020
♪How I wish time would stop right here♪

783
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:33,820
♪Get stuck in sweet silence♪

784
00:36:43,000 --> 00:36:43,590
There you are.

785
00:36:43,710 --> 00:36:44,400
How many of you?

786
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:45,030
Three.

787
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,480
How about that table?

788
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:49,360
But we always take this table.

789
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:51,440
It’s a table of six, you know.

790
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:53,590
But only three of you...

791
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,440
AC is over there.

792
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,030
Come on.

793
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:04,760
Make your order and then tell me.

794
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,030
Come on.

795
00:37:10,590 --> 00:37:11,150
Here.

796
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:21,950
Be seated, please. I’ll be quick.

797
00:37:22,070 --> 00:37:22,630
Sir.

798
00:37:23,150 --> 00:37:23,710
Come on.

799
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:26,630
All right. Be right there.

800
00:37:27,030 --> 00:37:29,510
When the dishes come, eat more.

801
00:37:31,480 --> 00:37:32,230
What do you mean?

802
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:35,000
Just get to the point.

803
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:36,510
Don’t beat about the bush.

804
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:40,840
You don’t say it, huh?

805
00:37:42,510 --> 00:37:44,000
Yun Xiang, you say it.

806
00:37:45,710 --> 00:37:48,880
We just want you
to communicate with Chief.

807
00:37:52,190 --> 00:37:54,190
Why must you bicker?

808
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:56,070
Who bickers with him?

809
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,550
What can I communicate?

810
00:37:58,190 --> 00:37:59,480
If you don’t communicate,

811
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:01,960
Jiang Yuan and I
will be too embarrassed.

812
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:02,710
Yeah.

813
00:38:03,030 --> 00:38:04,630
We can’t even have the big table
for barbecue.

814
00:38:04,630 --> 00:38:05,480
Yeah. He’s right.

815
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:13,880
Go get a table.

816
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,000
I’ll go wash my hands first.

817
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:15,670
All right.

818
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:16,230
Go ahead.

819
00:38:22,110 --> 00:38:22,710
Chief?

820
00:38:34,150 --> 00:38:34,710
Chuan.

821
00:38:38,710 --> 00:38:39,320
I’m full.

822
00:38:42,110 --> 00:38:43,670
Are you not going to talk to me anymore?

823
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:52,150
I’m fully full.

824
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:56,710
I know changing my application
has upset you.

825
00:38:57,880 --> 00:38:59,000
But it doesn’t mean
I don’t care about you.

826
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:01,840
I want us to be better.

827
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:05,880
All right.

828
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:09,190
I feel happy for you
when you have a higher goal.

829
00:39:09,550 --> 00:39:10,480
I support you.

830
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:11,760
Isn’t that enough?

831
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:13,630
If you really supported me,
you wouldn’t behave like this.

832
00:39:14,510 --> 00:39:16,400
I never mean to leave you alone.

833
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:18,800
We can go there together.

834
00:39:19,550 --> 00:39:20,960
Why must I go with you?

835
00:39:22,590 --> 00:39:24,400
Let alone whether I can be admitted
to Huatsing.

836
00:39:24,710 --> 00:39:26,190
